Changes in Guile DBI 2.0.0:

* 2.0.0 remove deprecated guile 1.6 api to work with 1.8.


Changes in Guile DBI 1.0.4:

* 1.0.3 actually never release becouse another compiling broke bug
  found. Fixed in this release.


Changes in Guile DBI 1.0.3:

* Fix include path search, this was braking compilation.


Changes in Guile DBI 1.0.2:

* Minor fix


Changes in Guile DBI 1.0.1:

* Implement test framework using greg.
* Fix double close bug introducing a booleand field in db handler
  struct.



Changes in Guile DBI 1.0.1:

* Assign copyright to FSF.
